{"tid":1082460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【靠害】推友落橋累對方重傷 18歲少女判監2日","createTime":"2019-03-29T03:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T23:41:02.000Z","uid":58851,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ef40a168751444d124f88dcf23d614ca9df5dae3","tid":1082460,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:28:33.000Z","msg":"美國華盛頓州少女去年被朋友推落橋事件，19歲女元兇周三被判監2日及38天社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n史密斯（Taylor Smith）去年8月將站在亞科爾特（Yacolt）劉易斯河上橋邊準備跳水的16歲朋友霍爾格森（Jordan Holgerson），一手推落橋，令霍爾格森由60呎高墮河受傷，五條肋骨折斷，肺部受傷，另有多處擦傷。<br />\n<br />\n霍爾格森被推落橋的片段在網上廣傳，史密斯被各方指摘。<br />\n<br />\n史密斯上月承認魯莽危害罪，在法官宣讀判刑時落淚。法官說她要為霍爾格森的重傷而受些牢獄之苦。她被戴上手扣帶走哭了出來。<br />\n<br />\n霍爾格森的媽媽吉妮爾（Genelle Holgerson）向法官表示，為女兒生還感到幸運，希望判史密斯入獄，指事件不但令她們一家破財，還飽受精神壓力。"},{"pid":"f46fa043379e4eeb9815567b148274a0563b684d","tid":1082460,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:28:58.000Z","msg":"新聞網址<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190329/59424944\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190329%2F59424944&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=37473078\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190329%2F59424944&h=ad337d6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190329/59424944</a>"},{"pid":"830fa6ab3d95c2b85645229bb9301eb7a3a852ba","tid":1082460,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190329/large/1553820902_baea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190329%2Flarge%2F1553820902_baea.jpg&h=1aa4042c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38e9b214e2e7908d9d2413f99dde3e70f12fe9c8","tid":1082460,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dis