/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你係咪係地鐵周圍走係咁屌人老母個D？係咪成日覺得有人背後講你，影你相？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你做乜停藥呀？又病發啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2945e96995db2d465208c8ff5058ee9ea1d0143","tid":1082460,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T14:37:06.000Z","msg":"唔好意思, 政府無能, Andante 精神病病發, 又可以上網<br />\n我唔小心踢爆佢精神病病重, 就開始發神經推舊POST"},{"pid":"17f012db85ff47cade9ea2994e8863b63644e084","tid":1082460,"uid":242630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2945e96995db2d465208c8ff5058ee9ea1d0143","tid":1082460,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T14:37:06.000Z","msg":"唔好意思, 政府無能, Andante 精神病病發, 又可以上網<br />\n我唔小心踢爆佢精神病病重, 就開始發神經推舊POST"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T23:41:02.000Z","msg":"少見的百摺短裙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/52796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/52796</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n嘩我屌你老母呀倚癲淘紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好以後改左名起唔亞你底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你個癲佬周街吊住女仔尾影腳？唔好咁痴線 你食藥啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係懷疑你日日係西鐵影學生妹校服裙底<br />\n你條友已經谷到變態，又有精神病，你係咪成日想強姦人？你係咪有孌童癖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都完全明白曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}